<div id="tv-confirm-modal" class="modal-overlay">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-title">🌐 External Page</div>
        <div class="modal-text">
            <p>You're about to leave this menu to an external web page.</p>
            <p class="modal-tip">💡 <span class="highlight-blue">Tip:</span> Enable your SL viewer's browser navigation bar first, so you can use Back/Forward freely.</p>
            <p class="modal-note">⚠️ Without it enabled, the only way back to this menu is turning the TV off and on again.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-buttons">
            <button class="modal-btn btn-confirm" onclick="confirmNavigation()">Proceed</button>
            <button class="modal-btn btn-cancel" onclick="closeModal()">Cancel</button>
        </div>
